{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">R\u00e9volte d\u2019Absalom<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. 1 R 1:5-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s cela, Absalom se procura un char et des chevaux, et cinquante hommes qui couraient devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.2","name":"2 Samuel 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.33","name":"2 Samuel 14:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il se levait de bon matin, et se tenait au bord du chemin de la porte. Et chaque fois qu\u2019un homme ayant une contestation se rendait vers le roi pour obtenir un jugement, Absalom l\u2019appelait, et disait: De quelle ville es-tu? Lorsqu\u2019il avait r\u00e9pondu: Je suis d\u2019une telle tribu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.3","name":"2 Samuel 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.1","name":"2 Samuel 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Absalom lui disait: Vois, ta cause est bonne et juste; mais personne de chez le roi ne t\u2019\u00e9coutera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.4","name":"2 Samuel 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.2","name":"2 Samuel 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Absalom disait: Qui m\u2019\u00e9tablira juge dans le pays? Tout homme qui aurait une contestation et un proc\u00e8s viendrait \u00e0 moi, et je lui ferais justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.5","name":"2 Samuel 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.3","name":"2 Samuel 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et quand quelqu\u2019un s\u2019approchait pour se prosterner devant lui, il lui tendait la main, le saisissait et l\u2019embrassait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.6","name":"2 Samuel 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.4","name":"2 Samuel 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Absalom agissait ainsi \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de tous ceux d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui se rendaient vers le roi pour demander justice. Et Absalom gagnait le c\u0153ur des gens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.7","name":"2 Samuel 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.5","name":"2 Samuel 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Au bout de quarante ans, Absalom dit au roi: Permets que j\u2019aille \u00e0 H\u00e9bron, pour accomplir le v\u0153u que j\u2019ai fait \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.8","name":"2 Samuel 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.6","name":"2 Samuel 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Car ton serviteur a fait un v\u0153u, pendant que je demeurais \u00e0 Gueschur en Syrie; j\u2019ai dit: Si l\u2019\u00c9ternel me ram\u00e8ne \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, je servirai l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.9","name":"2 Samuel 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.7","name":"2 Samuel 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le roi lui dit: Va en paix. Et Absalom se leva et partit pour H\u00e9bron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.10","name":"2 Samuel 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.8","name":"2 Samuel 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Absalom envoya des espions dans toutes les tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour dire: Quand vous entendrez le son de la trompette, vous direz: Absalom r\u00e8gne \u00e0 H\u00e9bron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.11","name":"2 Samuel 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.9","name":"2 Samuel 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Deux cents hommes de J\u00e9rusalem, qui avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 invit\u00e9s, accompagn\u00e8rent Absalom; et ils le firent en toute simplicit\u00e9, sans rien savoir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.12","name":"2 Samuel 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.10","name":"2 Samuel 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Pendant qu\u2019Absalom offrait les sacrifices, il envoya chercher \u00e0 la ville de Guilo Achitophel, le Guilonite, conseiller de David. La conjuration devint puissante, et le peuple \u00e9tait de plus en plus nombreux aupr\u00e8s d\u2019Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.13","name":"2 Samuel 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.11","name":"2 Samuel 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Fuite de David. Entr\u00e9e d\u2019Absalom dans J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-37: cf. Ps 3. (2 S 16:15-23; 17:1-23.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Quelqu\u2019un vint informer David, et lui dit: Le c\u0153ur des hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019est tourn\u00e9 vers Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.14","name":"2 Samuel 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.12","name":"2 Samuel 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et David dit \u00e0 tous ses serviteurs qui \u00e9taient avec lui \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem: Levez-vous, fuyons, car il n\u2019y aura point de salut pour nous devant Absalom. H\u00e2tez-vous de partir; sinon, il ne tarderait pas \u00e0 nous atteindre, et il nous pr\u00e9cipiterait dans le malheur et frapperait la ville du tranchant de l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.15","name":"2 Samuel 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.13","name":"2 Samuel 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Les serviteurs du roi lui dirent: Tes serviteurs feront tout ce que voudra mon seigneur le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.16","name":"2 Samuel 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.14","name":"2 Samuel 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le roi sortit, et toute sa maison le suivait, et il laissa dix concubines pour garder la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.17","name":"2 Samuel 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.15","name":"2 Samuel 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Le roi sortit, et tout le peuple le suivait, et ils s\u2019arr\u00eat\u00e8rent \u00e0 la derni\u00e8re maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.18","name":"2 Samuel 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.16","name":"2 Samuel 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Tous ses serviteurs, tous les K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens et tous les P\u00e9l\u00e9thiens, pass\u00e8rent \u00e0 ses c\u00f4t\u00e9s; et tous les Gathiens, au nombre de six cents hommes, venus de Gath \u00e0 sa suite, pass\u00e8rent devant le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.19","name":"2 Samuel 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.17","name":"2 Samuel 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Itta\u00ef de Gath: Pourquoi viendrais-tu aussi avec nous? Retourne, et reste avec le roi, car tu es \u00e9tranger, et m\u00eame tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 emmen\u00e9 de ton pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.20","name":"2 Samuel 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.18","name":"2 Samuel 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Tu es arriv\u00e9 d\u2019hier, et aujourd\u2019hui je te ferais errer avec nous \u00e7\u00e0 et l\u00e0, quand je ne sais moi-m\u00eame o\u00f9 je vais! Retourne, et emm\u00e8ne tes fr\u00e8res avec toi. Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel use envers toi de bont\u00e9 et de fid\u00e9lit\u00e9!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.21","name":"2 Samuel 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.19","name":"2 Samuel 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Itta\u00ef r\u00e9pondit au roi, et dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant et mon seigneur le roi est vivant! Au lieu o\u00f9 sera mon seigneur le roi, soit pour mourir, soit pour vivre, l\u00e0 aussi sera ton serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.22","name":"2 Samuel 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.20","name":"2 Samuel 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>David dit alors \u00e0 Itta\u00ef: Va, passe! Et Itta\u00ef de Gath passa, avec tous ses gens et tous les enfants qui \u00e9taient avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.23","name":"2 Samuel 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.21","name":"2 Samuel 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Toute la contr\u00e9e \u00e9tait en larmes et l\u2019on poussait de grands cris, au passage de tout le peuple. Le roi passa le torrent de C\u00e9dron, et tout le peuple passa vis-\u00e0-vis du chemin qui m\u00e8ne au d\u00e9sert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.24","name":"2 Samuel 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.22","name":"2 Samuel 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Tsadok \u00e9tait aussi l\u00e0, et avec lui tous les L\u00e9vites portant l\u2019arche de l\u2019alliance de Dieu; et ils pos\u00e8rent l\u2019arche de Dieu, et Abiathar montait, pendant que tout le peuple achevait de sortir de la ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.25","name":"2 Samuel 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.23","name":"2 Samuel 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Tsadok: Reporte l\u2019arche de Dieu dans la ville. Si je trouve gr\u00e2ce aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, il me ram\u00e8nera, et il me fera voir l\u2019arche et sa demeure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.26","name":"2 Samuel 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.24","name":"2 Samuel 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.26","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:26","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Mais s\u2019il dit: Je ne prends point plaisir en toi! Me voici, qu\u2019il me fasse ce qui lui semblera bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.27","name":"2 Samuel 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.25","name":"2 Samuel 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.27","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:27","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Le roi dit encore au sacrificateur Tsadok: Comprends-tu? Retourne en paix dans la ville, avec Achimaats, ton fils, et avec Jonathan, fils d\u2019Abiathar, vos deux fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.28","name":"2 Samuel 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.26","name":"2 Samuel 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.28","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:28","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Voyez, j\u2019attendrai dans les plaines du d\u00e9sert, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il m\u2019arrive des nouvelles de votre part.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.29","name":"2 Samuel 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.27","name":"2 Samuel 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.29","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:29","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Ainsi Tsadok et Abiathar report\u00e8rent l\u2019arche de Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et ils y rest\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.30","name":"2 Samuel 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.28","name":"2 Samuel 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.30","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:30","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>David monta la colline des oliviers. Il montait en pleurant et la t\u00eate couverte, et il marchait nu-pieds; et tous ceux qui \u00e9taient avec lui se couvrirent aussi la t\u00eate, et ils montaient en pleurant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.31","name":"2 Samuel 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.29","name":"2 Samuel 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.31","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:31","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>On vint dire \u00e0 David: Achitophel est avec Absalom parmi les conjur\u00e9s. Et David dit: O \u00c9ternel, r\u00e9duis \u00e0 n\u00e9ant les conseils d\u2019Achitophel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.32","name":"2 Samuel 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.30","name":"2 Samuel 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.32","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:32","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Lorsque David fut arriv\u00e9 au sommet, o\u00f9 il se prosterna devant Dieu, voici, Huscha\u00ef, l\u2019Arkien, vint au-devant de lui, la tunique d\u00e9chir\u00e9e et la t\u00eate couverte de terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.33","name":"2 Samuel 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.31","name":"2 Samuel 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.33","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:33","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>David lui dit: Si tu viens avec moi, tu me seras \u00e0 charge.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.34","name":"2 Samuel 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.32","name":"2 Samuel 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.34","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:34","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Et, au contraire, tu an\u00e9antiras en ma faveur les conseils d\u2019Achitophel, si tu retournes \u00e0 la ville, et que tu dises \u00e0 Absalom: O roi, je serai ton serviteur; je fus autrefois le serviteur de ton p\u00e8re, mais je suis maintenant ton serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.35","name":"2 Samuel 15:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.33","name":"2 Samuel 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.35","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:35","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs Tsadok et Abiathar ne seront-ils pas l\u00e0 avec toi? Tout ce que tu apprendras de la maison du roi, tu le diras aux sacrificateurs Tsadok et Abiathar.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.36","name":"2 Samuel 15:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.34","name":"2 Samuel 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.36","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:36","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Et comme ils ont l\u00e0 aupr\u00e8s d\u2019eux leurs deux fils, Achimaats, fils de Tsadok, et Jonathan, fils d\u2019Abiathar, c\u2019est par eux que vous me ferez savoir tout ce que vous aurez appris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.37","name":"2 Samuel 15:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.35","name":"2 Samuel 15:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.37","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 15:37","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.15.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Huscha\u00ef, ami de David, retourna donc \u00e0 la ville. Et Absalom entra dans J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15","name":"2 Samuel 15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.1","name":"2 Samuel 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.36","name":"2 Samuel 15:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb34bdd66.63336582');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34bdd66.63336582\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb34bdd66.63336582","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb34bdd66.63336582'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34bdd66.63336582\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}